data.description: Beautifully kept total electric home with new roof, new exterior paint, new interior paint, new back deck, fireplace, bonus room, and full unfinished basement! All living space other than the finished bonus is on the main level, and it features a split bedroom plan. Back yard is fenced, full poured wall basement has a great boat door, and you're located on a small cul de sac with almost no traffic.
